Corporate Headfitters Limited is a fashion design company that is into the production clothing and Millinery items. The company represented 3 distinct brands; a high-end couture millinery brand, A low to mid-range millinery brand and a low to mid-range Afrocentric clothing line. For almost 3 decades, they have dressed celebrities and fashion forward women in the society and abroad. We are recruiting to fill the vacant position below: Job Title: Account Officer Location: Lagos

